projectName: Design Thinking Project — Food Waste App
comment: This project is about a food waste at home. Through user interviews and empathy mapping I  identified key pain points such as forgetting expiry dates and not knowing what to cook. Using methods that the teacher told us about and flow mapping I developed a concept for a simple app that can help users log groceries, receive expiry notifications and get recipe suggestions. The MVP focuses on the core features and with future steps including shared accounts and savings tracking.
